{
  "text": "However, a central part of design quality is expressed as the building form, internal and [CITATION_1] . Space design quality and its importance to sustainable construction: The case of hospital buildings. Portugal SB13-contribution of sustainable building to meet EU 20-20-20 targets. ''The proposal is to divide criteria in three dimensions (environmental, social and functional, and economical) and incorporate the indoor and outdoor spaces design quality especially in the sociocultural and functional quality category'' Design Quality Indicator for Health. (2015) . Construction Industry Council, London. ''Design quality outlined as build quality (construction, engineering), functionality (access, space, use), and impact (form, materials, urban and social integration.' [CITATION_2] . Therapy by design: Evaluating the UK hospital building program. Health and Place.",
